import React from 'react';
import {
  Container,
  Typography,
  Box,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  Grid,
  Button,
} from '@mui/material';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';

const Dashboard: React.FC = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();

  const handleLogout = () => {
    navigate('/login');
  };

  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg">
      <Box sx={{ mt: 4, mb: 4 }}>
        <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 4 }}>
          <Typography variant="h4" component="h1">
            Dashboard
          </Typography>
          <Button variant="outlined" onClick={handleLogout}>
            Logout
          </Button>
        </Box>
        
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                  BMI
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="h4" color="primary">
                  22.5
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Normal weight
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                  Current Weight
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="h4" color="primary">
                  70 kg
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                  Daily Calories
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="h4" color="secondary">
                  2000
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  kcal goal
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Typography variant="h6" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                  Daily Protein
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ color: 'success.main' }}>
                  140g
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  protein goal
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        <Box sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
          <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
            Welcome to CalorieFit!
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
            This is your fitness dashboard. Here you can track your progress, 
            manage your diet, and monitor your exercise routines.
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
            API is running on: http://localhost:5263
          </Typography>
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Dashboard;
